title: Don
subTitle: Chakaravarthi, a wayward college student searching for purpose, navigates campus life while grappling with a controlling father and a strict professor.

title: Surya Ka Yaarana
subTitle: A soldier going on a rescue mission, hears about his father's death by lung cancer and mournfully looks back on his memories of how he helped him in matters of love and life.

title: Jigar Kaleja
subTitle: A short tempered cab driver, Raju, unwillingly becomes the saviour of a village. When an industrialist tries to drive away the villagers by polluting their water and air, Raju steps up to help them.

title: Inttelligent
subTitle: A successful software engineer becomes a vigilante following the demise of his mentor in a bid to seek revenge against those responsible for the latter's death.

title: Main Hoon Dandadhikari
subTitle: Following his father's death, a man gives up on his dream to become a film-maker and joins the police force. He then attempts to track down a psychopathic killer who targets schoolgirls.

title: Kadamban
subTitle: Kadamban lives a peaceful life with the villagers in a remote forest in Tamil Nadu. Things take a turn when a business tycoon decides to drive his tribe out of the area in order to extract minerals.

title: Vivegam
subTitle: Ajay Kumar, a former counter-terrorism agent, is called for a special mission. However, he is betrayed by his friends and is accused of extremely treasonous acts.

title: Guardian
subTitle: An unavenged woman returns from the dead to terrify and terrorise those who tormented her when she was alive.

title: Gally Rowdy
subTitle: A young man tries to find a balance between his love interest and friends. Meanwhile, his friends convince him to stay rowdy.

title: Ek Aur Vinashak
subTitle: An honest man is forced to turn into a gangster as he strives to make enough money for the treatment of a girl who is comatose.

title: Ek Aur Vinashak
subTitle: An honest man is forced to turn into a gangster as he strives to make enough money for the treatment of a girl who is comatose.

title: Ek Aur Bol Bachchan
subTitle: A man and his sister move to a village where a local landlord employs him at his house. Since he pretends to be of a different faith, he faces trouble while keeping up this lie.

title: Mahabali Bal Ganesh VI
subTitle: Top, Dhoti and Suitboot land on Kailash Parbat where they meet Nandi and Mooshak Raj. There, they come across stories about Bal Ganesh, who fights to rid the world of demons.

title: Mufti
subTitle: Gana, a police officer, must go undercover to find and kill Bhairathi Ranagal, a crime lord. However, when he realises that Bhairathi's intentions are good, he needs to decide his next step.

title: Thadam
subTitle: While investigating the death of a man, the police track down their lead suspect. However, the case takes a twisted turn when they discover a clone of their suspect.

title: Roberrt
subTitle: Raghava, the head cook in a catering unit, leads a peaceful life with his son Arjun. However, their bliss is short-lived as Raghava's past comes back to haunt him.

title: Kali Kitaab
subTitle: When narratives from a cryptic book spring to life, a woman experiences bizarre phenomena and resolves to uncover the identity of its enigmatic writer.

title: Yashoda
subTitle: Surrogate mother Yashodha is advised to follow a few guidelines to keep herself and her baby healthy and safe. However, something happens at the surrogate centre that puts both of them at risk.

title: Buddy
subTitle: A terrible accident leaves Pallavi in a coma while her soul possesses the body of a teddy bear. With her organs in danger of being traded, she enlists the help of a pilot, Aditya.

title: The Return Of Lion
subTitle: When a social worker dies, his son must not only avenge his death but also prove his innocence when the welfare fund money accumulated by his family goes missing.

title: Conjuring Kannappan
subTitle: When a man plucks a feather off a dreamcatcher, he has nightmares where injuries reflect in the real world. But when this affects his family and friends, they decide to find the root of the problem.

title: Conjuring Kannappan
subTitle: When a man plucks a feather off a dreamcatcher, he has nightmares where injuries reflect in the real world. But when this affects his family and friends, they decide to find the root of the problem.

title: Super Ranga
subTitle: Ranga, a reckless thrill-seeker, falls in love with Swathi who makes him promise to be more responsible. However, she breaks up with him when he goes back to his old ways.

title: Naagin Bani Suhaagan
subTitle: Vaishali, an ardent devotee of Lord Shiva, is blessed with a boon to transform herself into a shapeshifting snake. She falls into a dilemma when circumstances force her to go against her love.

title: F2: Fun and Frustration
subTitle: Two young men hope to control their wives after their respective marriages. However, their chauvinistic attitude often lands them in hilarious situations.

title: Harom Hara (The Revolt)
subTitle: Subrahmanyam loses his job and faces financial ruin. In an attempt to overcome his limitations, he gets involved in the illegal arms trade, eventually becoming one of South India's notorious arms dealers.

title: Angel
subTitle: Nani discovers a rare antique idol from the excavation site at Amaravati. He wants to sell it and keep the money for himself, but before he can do that, the idol goes missing.

title: Jawaan
subTitle: Yellapragada Jai, an honest man, faces challenges when his childhood friend, Keshava, becomes a criminal. To protect his country, Jai puts everything on the line to thwart Keshava's perilous plans.

title: Yudh Ek Jung
subTitle: Chandu, a supermarket employee, encounters trouble when he decides to help Indu, an aspiring actress, and gets embroiled in a murder case.

title: Gajaana
subTitle: On an adventurous search for treasure in the dense forest, a group of young explorers soon discovers they have become the quarry.

title: RDX
subTitle: Robert, Dony and Xavier grow up together while honing their fighting skills. However, after an incident separates them for several years, an attack on their family reunites the three friends.

title: Munduvareda Adhyaya
subTitle: ACP Bala is in charge of investigating a prominent figure's mysterious murder. However, the mystery keeps getting even more complicated with each reveal instead of taking him closer to the criminal.
